Castilla Says He Favors Sol-Denominated Peruvian Debt Sales

-- B y   J o h n   Q u i g l e y
-- 
2011-09-21T19:08:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/castilla-says-he-favors-sol-denominated-peruvian-debt-sales.html
Peru ’s Finance Minister Miguel
Castilla said debt markets are currently “too volatile” for
the country to raise the financing it needs for next year.  Speaking during a news conference at  New York ’s Princeton
Club, Castilla said the government hasn’t taken a decision on
issuance though his preference is for a sale of sol-denominated
bonds.  To contact the reporter on this story:
John Quigley in Lima at 
